    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1890-09-11T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1890-09-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="92"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d92">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Mizner</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1890-09-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">September</hi> 11, 1890</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Mizner telegraphs through Mr. Ryan, announcing the complete compliance with
                    the bases of peace and the disbandment of the armies, and stating that the
                    presence of the vessels of war are no longer required.</p>
            </div>
